  EffectDiscription_ENG: "\uFF1CBarrier\uFF1E \n\uFF1CPartition ([Angewomon] & [LadyDevimon])\uFF1E
    \n[When Digivolving] You may play 1 level 5 or lower yellow or purple card from
    your hand or trash without paying the cost. Then, if this Digimon's stack has
    2 or more same-level cards, trash the top cards of both players' security stacks
    so that they have 3 cards left.\n[All Turns] [Once Per Turn] When security stacks
    are removed from, you may place 1 Digimon as the bottom security card."
